This software includes smart contracts that interact with blockchain networks
and decentralized finance (DeFi) protocols. These contracts may handle user
funds, tokens, and other digital assets.

THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. The authors
and copyright holders:

1. DO NOT WARRANT that the smart contracts are free from bugs, errors, or
